{"tid":265842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"朦著耳朵 那裡那天不再聽到在呼號的人","createTime":"2017-06-01T03:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T01:45:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30c64c6ef54e0408d0ec63f45a69fbc1f8fe6d6c","tid":265842,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"朦著耳朵 那裡那天不再聽到在呼號的人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBeyond&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n長城<br />\n作詞：劉卓輝<br />\n作曲：黃家駒<br />\n<br />\n遙遠的東方 遼闊的邊疆 還有遠古的破牆<br />\n前世的滄桑 後世的風光 萬里千山牢牢接壤<br />\n圍著老去的國度 圍著事實的真相<br />\n圍著浩瀚的歲月 圍著慾望與理想<br />\n迷信的村莊 神秘的中央 還有昨天的戰場<br />\n皇帝的新衣 熱血的纓槍 誰卻甘心流連塞上<br />\n<br />\n圍著老去的國度 圍著事實的真相<br />\n圍著浩瀚的歲月 圍著慾望與理想(叫嚷)<br />\n<br />\n朦著耳朵 那裡那天不再聽到在呼號的人(像呼號神)<br />\nWOO AH WOO AH AH AH 朦著眼睛<br />\n再見往昔景仰的那樣一道疤痕<br />\nWOO AH WOO AH AH AH 留在地殼頭上<br />\n無冕的身軀 忘我的思想 還有顯赫的破牆<br />\n誰也衝不開 誰也拋不低 誰要一生流離浪蕩"},{"pid":"96d3fd116559ba808c9684d4fb15fcb52259d1b6","tid":265842,"uid":15863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"如黃家駒當年冇死，今日肯定係個大中華膠<br />\n唔明點解會有人ff佢會帶領人抗爭<br />\n唱今天我唱到懵左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0730d4a48eccc55f39dfc2bd20740ad219a3b8af","tid":265842,"uid":104822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"在下孤陋寡聞<br />\n呢首歌唔係諷刺中國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3481b923abf57c5210f6f0a4adad516d49a91b90","tid":265842,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"長城 - Beyond (2009)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ub0UMPJ3wtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fub0UMPJ3wtg&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0d28522d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ub0UMPJ3wtg</a>"},{"pid":"d8aeeb1503f5f7ba6b5248bddd0101a6d175b31d","tid":265842,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T